        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;United States Commission on International Religious Freedom Reauthorization Act of 2025&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill reauthorizes the U.S. Commission on International Religious Freedom through FY2028. The commission is an independent federal commission tasked with monitoring international religious freedom conditions, reviewing U.S. government policy, and making policy recommendations.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
